----------------------------------------------------------------------
openWakeWord pre-trained feature models — NonCommercial (IMPORTANT)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The trained wake models in ../out/final/*.onnx run on top of openWakeWord's
shared feature models (melspectrogram.onnx and embedding_model.onnx, fetched by
../download_features.py). Per the openWakeWord project, those pre-trained
feature components are licensed CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 (NonCommercial) due to their
training-data terms, whereas openWakeWord's *code* is Apache-2.0. The
NonCommercial restriction therefore applies to the wake-word feature stack,
not to Talker's own (MIT) code. Review this before any commercial use of the
wake-word feature.
